d \u00e5 si noe som helst om kreften de f\u00f8rste to \u00e5rene, sier Hans Petter Andersen, som uten \u00e5 blunke sp\u00e5r kong \u00bfHarald en lys framtid. - Vi kommer nok til \u00e5 ha den samme kongen lenge enn\u00e5. Selv har jeg levd fire \u00e5r etter operasjonen, og jeg har tenkt \u00e5 g\u00e5 p\u00e5 en ny periode, ler han"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "8951373b2d0763078cba0485aabbba61b213cae52a1da946d9396de902c67807"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-02-21T19:05:48.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Bl\u00e6rekreftopererte Hans Petter Andersen (73) tror kongens \u00e5penhet rundt sykdommen kan rive ned tabuer og gj\u00f8re diagnosen lettere \u00e5 b\u00e6re for mange."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1079198.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/ver2%20kronprinsparet_mindre"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/b9b6e481cb042a441b882f1b7744774465b05a98.jpg?595bb736"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "- Det vil g\u00e5 fint -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "b9b6e481cb042a441b882f1b7744774465b05a98"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "health-and-fitness"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": "kong"}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["harald", "hans petter andersen", "hans petter"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "trondheim"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1079198.ece5/ALTERN